Semifinals
04/Mar Vitória 0-0 Bahia
04/Mar Itabuna 1-1 Galícia
08/Mar Bahia 2-0 Vitória
08/Mar Galícia 2-0 Itabuna
FINAL
11/Mar Galícia 0-1 Bahia
18/Mar Bahia 1-0 Galícia
Bahia, as champions of 1º Turno, is classified to the Final Phase with two
bonus points; Galícia, as runner-up, is also classified to the Final Phase
with one bonus point.
