Semifinals
18/Apr Galícia 1-1 Bahia
18/Apr Vitória 0-0 Fluminense
22/Apr Fluminense 0-0 Vitória  [0-1 on extra time]
22/Apr Bahia 0-0 Galícia       [1-0 on extra time]
Final
25/Apr Vitória 0-2 Bahia
29/Apr Bahia 1-1 Vitória
Bahia, as champions of 2º Turno and already classified to the Final Phase,
wins more two bonus points; Vitória, as runner-up, is also classified to the
Final Phase with one bonus point.
Total of Points (Without Quadrangulares)
 1. Bahia                   15   already classified to Final Phase
 2. Fluminense           13   classified to Final Phase
 3. Galícia               12   already classified to Final Phase
 4. Itabuna              12
 5. Vitória              10   already classified to Final Phase
 6. Serrano               7
 7. Atlético              6
 7. Catuense              6
 7. Jacuipense            6
---------------------------
10. Leônico               3   relegated
Final Phase
Bahia entered with 4 bonus points due to had won both Turnos; Galícia and
Vitória entered with 1 bonus point due to each one had been runner-up of
one Turno.
